How Node based web servers are different from traditional web servers?
opts: Node based server process request much faster than traditional server.
Node based server uses a single threaded model and can services much larger number of requests than traditional server like Apache HTTP Server.

questions.title: Which of the following is true about exec methd of child_process module.
opts: The exec() method runs a command in a shell and buffers the output.
The exec() method returns a buffer with a max size.
The exec() method waits for the process to end and tries to return all the buffered data at once.
